				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">If a wake the dead pet can slow unslowable mobs....which, I've heard, they can.......
<br />

<br />

<br />
Is it possible to give a WTD pet a weapon that procs "slow" and then get aggro on some Uber duber mob....while he's pounding you .. pet slows it....with the weapon.....
<br />

<br />
Just curious, if it's ever been done/thought of before. 
<br />

<br />
Be nice, for some encounters, heh.
<br />

<br />
I'm thinking, heh, /duel a caster, send WTD pet on caster, caster gates, give WTD pet slow weapon, get aggro on uber, duber mob....and then.. hey, slowed uber duber mob.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
