				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Well what if ya dueled an other pet class(Let's say an SK) with <span style="font-weight: bold">/hold</span> AA. Here how this could work.
<br />

<br />
1- Get the SK to cast their Lowest pet.
<br />
2- Get WIZZY to TL the pet person ya gonna dual. (Or just gate vice TL)
<br />
3- Necro and SK do the magic /d command
<br />
4- Click your WTD button on the SK's pet
<br />
5- SK click the TL "Yes" Button (or gate if avail -potions, bla,bla)
<br />
6- Now ya WTD pet is free to get weapons and stuff.
<br />
7- Do your Harmshield and sit close by to mob so ya get hit.
<br />
8- Send pet while sitting (don't get up he'll come) then once ya get hit ya WTD will hammer at that boss
<br />
9- So step 1 to 8 should take ya less then 30 sec. But at worst call it 30 sec, it leaves ya 60 sec of him trying to proc SLOW (or Cast Slow if was shammy or something)
<br />

<br />
If ya don't wanna die on a UBER dude i guest that's how i'd do it in PERFECT condition.
<br />

<br />
Worst, just do all step up to 5 then just LB on the mob so he summon ya that'll get his attention and then HS. Not sure how THAT would work but well ... ... errr could work. Hehehe sure will get the MOB the attention.<br />_________________<br /><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: normal"><span style="color: darkred">Virun Waulfebane</span></span>
<br />
<span style="color: red">Adept Vampire</span>
